---
title: Pork Ragù with Orzo and Cheesy Toasts
description: In this meal, savoury pork, spinach and crushed tomatoes are the building blocks of a delicious sauce that gets paired with buttery orzo pasta. We can't forget a side of cheesy garlic bread for scooping up every morsel!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragu-au-porc-6f0bdea9.jpg
